NEA 11.6.0.122 
Once the ANALYZE HISTORICAL PASSWORDS was disabled the report makes more since as to what the last scan is displaying.

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor v11.6 > Solutions > Active Directory Solution > 2.Users Job Group> AD_WeakPasswords Job
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Solutions/ActiveDirectory/Users/AD_WeakPasswords.htm

We looked at the Full report for Weak Passwords: Weak Historical Password - the listed accounts have a historical password that was found in the dictionary
This was also maintaining the history of the Shares Common Password – Account shares a password with another account
